data.description: Welcome home to 3025 Washington Rd! This charming fully renovated ranch on sits on a large level lot ready for its new owner and has NO HOA. Not a fan of carpet? No worries this home has beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Ready to spend family time? Retreat to the spacious family room with a tray ceiling, recessed lighting and beautiful wood burning fireplace for cold winter nights. There is a sunroom off of the family room with a brick accent wall that is perfect for a home office. The remodeled kitchen has granite countertops and stainless steel appliances ready to prepare the perfect meals. The spacious dining area is off of the kitchen and ready to accommodate large family gatherings. The oversized owners suite has a cathedral ceiling, large closet and the en suite has a tiled walk in shower. There are 2 additional oversized bedrooms and full bath on the opposite side of the owners suite providing additional privacy. There is an electric car charger that stays with the property. This home is conveniently located close to airport, shopping, and major highways. Don't hesitate to schedule your private tour today! Motivated seller bring all offers!$1000 towards closing cost given with preferred lender Nicole Thornton with Motto Mortgage.
